<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">嗨，<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你也注意到了嗎～？<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />昨天從<tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" /><tag a="110" b="13" /><delay20 />的家裡，<delay20 />
傳出了<tag a="135" b="7" arg="0xcd00" />的<delay8 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />香味喔～</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯，<delay20 />我昨天的確有在家裡製作點心，<delay8 />
不過你竟然能猜到是<tag a="135" b="7" arg="0xcd00" />，<delay20 />
<20_2 arg="7" /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是厲害耶。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">嘿嘿，<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />可別小瞧<delay20 />
我的鼻子喔～<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果是<tag a="135" b="7" arg="0xcd00" />的味道，<delay20 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不管離多遠<delay20 />
我都聞得出來喔～<anim id="Eh" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">真不愧是<tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" /><10_4 />
<20_2 arg="8" /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這次我試著在裝飾的部分<delay20 />
加了一點自己的創意喔。<pageBreak /><20_2 arg="7" /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />稍微多下了點功夫，<delay20 />
樣子就變得非常華麗，<delay20 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />成功做到「連外觀都很美味」的程度呢！<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦咦～？<delay20 />外觀也有味道嗎～！？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Smiling" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />如果只用看的就覺得很好吃，<delay20 />
那不管過多久都不會被吃完，<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感覺很棒耶～<anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這樣啊～<delay20 />光用看的都覺得好吃～<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Smiling" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />總覺得聽起來<delay8 />
會讓我更餓耶～<anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哇～<delay20 />聞起來就很香了～<delay20 />
那如果連看起來都好吃的話，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />味道一定更棒吧！？<anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">呵呵呵，<delay20 />那我下一次<delay20 />
就為<tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" /><delay20 />
真心誠意地做一份吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看起來<delay20 />很普通的也沒關係～<delay20 />
希望你可以快點做給我吃～<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而且<delay20 />真心誠意又吃不飽～<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="TakenAback" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />唉～</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，<delay20 />我問你喔～<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你有沒有什麼書可以推薦給我呢？</message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦！？<delay frames="40" /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，<delay20 />
你會看書嗎？<delay frames="40" />
總覺得有點意外呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想想喔，<delay frames="40" />雖然我不知道你的興趣是什麼，<delay20 />
但我讀完後還有印象的書大概是<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />《<tag a="135" b="0" arg="0xcd00" />》和<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />《<tag a="135" b="0" arg="0xcd01" />》吧。</message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯嗯，<delay20 />這樣啊～<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那<delay20 />你說的那兩本書，<delay20 />
<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哪一本比較厚啊？<anim id="Eh" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看來<delay20 />你是認真想讀書呢！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我認為是<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />《<tag a="135" b="0" arg="0xcd00" />》喔。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />它非常厚，而且內容發人深省呢！</message>
	<message label="105" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">啊，<delay20 />沒有啦～<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想說反正看了馬上就會睡著，<delay20 />
所以才想問你推薦用哪一本當枕頭～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="106" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="ColdChill" target="actor" targetSpec="" />原來是這樣啊。<delay frames="60" />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那《<tag a="135" b="0" arg="0xcd00" />》，<delay20 />
我想它的厚度應該足夠用來當枕頭呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="107" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="ColdChill" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這樣啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<delay frames="60" />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果要當枕頭的話，我應該會推薦<delay20 />
《<tag a="135" b="0" arg="0xcd01" />》喔。</message>
	<message label="201" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" /><tag a="110" b="13" />～<delay frames="40" />
跟我一起<delay20 />唱歌嘛～<delay frames="80" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啦～<delay20 />啦～<delay8 />啦～<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="202" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在外面唱歌實在是太害羞了，<delay20 />
我做不到呀！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過<delay8 />剛才的「<tag a="110" b="5" />」<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是<tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />的口頭禪吧？<anim id="FaintSmile" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="50" />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />聽起來很適合那首歌，<delay20 />我覺得很棒喔。<anim id="Aha" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="203" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真的～？<delay frames="40" />謝謝你～<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那<delay20 />如果你跟我用一樣的口頭禪，<delay20 />
或許就不會害羞了喔～<anim id="Eh" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="204" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">真、<delay20 />真的嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這樣的話，<delay20 />我嘗試一下好了。<delay frames="80" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那麼，<delay20 />咳咳<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />啦～<delay20 />啦哩～<delay8 />啦～<delay20 />
嚕～<delay20 />啦～<delay20 />啦～<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="205" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Clapping" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，<delay20 />唱得真好～！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />歌很棒，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />口頭禪感覺也不錯喔～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="Shocked" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="206" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">真的嗎！？<delay frames="40" /><anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />我好高興！<delay frames="40" />
難得有這個機會，<delay20 />
那我就繼續使用這個口頭禪囉，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>